@returns(200) A single definition for an email
@errors {400: Bad request, 403: Permission error, 500: Server Error}

@endpoint GET /messaging/v1/email/definitions/{definitionKey}
@desc getEmailDefinition
@required {definitionKey: any # Unique identifier of the definition to get}
@returns(200) Definition of email successfully retrieved
@errors {400: Bad request, 403: Permission error, 404: Not found, 500: Server Error}

